  <brief_title>Does Text Message Support After Discharge Improve Outcomes Following Bariatric Surgery? A Randomised Trial.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Does Text Message Support After Discharge Improve Outcomes Following Bariatric Surgery? A Randomised Trial and Sub-study of the BOBS Study (Better Outcomes Following Bariatric Surgery)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>University of Auckland, New Zealand</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
